    <h1 style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">About</h1>
    <p>Frontend engineer at Meituan, working on monitoring infrastructure (Raptor). Interested in AI agents, multi-agent systems, and building personal tools.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem;">This site is my public knowledge base — notes on things I'm learning, projects I'm building, and ideas worth writing down.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem; color:var(--color-muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em;">Links</h2>
    <ul style="list-style:none; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem;">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/mylesio">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Base>
